S  E  R  A  P  H 
Here's to our higher self.
I felt like mine began to stare back through the mirror as I painted, showing me a version of myself that has existed all along. By the time I finished, the sun was rising, and I felt sort of manic, almost destructive, like Kali. I felt firey and powerful. And then I washed it off. Body art is so healing.

👁👁👁👁👁👁
